    <item>
      <title>特朗普的选举谎言如何影响 2026 年中期选举</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/video/us/elections/100000010766599/trump-false-claim-election-stolen-impact-2026-midterms.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府利用联邦政府的力量支持他对 2020 年大选的虚假说法，以便在中期选举前调查关键的摇摆州。 《纽约时报》记者尼克·科拉萨尼蒂（Nick Corasaniti）专注于选举，他重点关注了成为主要目标的州及其原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/video/us/elections/100000010766599/trump-false-claim-election-stolen-impact-2026-midterms.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 19:30:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官驳回有关特朗普冻结隧道资金的大量诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/12/nyregion/gateway-hudson-tunnel-project-trump-funding.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官表示，此案基本上没有实际意义，因为政府已经恢复了暂时停止的超过 2 亿美元的资金流动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/12/nyregion/gateway-hudson-tunnel-project-trump-funding.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 19:22:08 GMT</pubDate>
